column45:
So instead, this gorgeous lady came
from the Kingdom to train under him,
and then the craziest thing happened!

column49:
Y no solo eso, mañana será tan maja
como siempre; pasado mañana, igual;
al día siguiente, lo mismo...

column45:
Oh, if only she'd greet me, too! Maybe
if I just casually cross her path... Oh,
but heaven forbid I obstruct her view!

I just gazed at them, drinking all the
while. Hanamori kept me company,
and we just kept slinging them back.
